    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have trained since your early days to master the art of puppetry, created by the first puppeteer in Sunagakure&#x27;s history, Chikamatsu Monzaemon. Because of that, your skills are naturally directed to the puppeteer path.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Community Compendium/Sunagakure Puppeteer.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Community Compendium</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 10+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 3 from Balance, Climb, Chakra Control, Craft (Mechanical), Hide, Knowledge (ninja lore), Listen, Ninjutsu, Sleight of Hand, Survival.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Craft Poison, Craft Puppets, Genin, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Resist Poisons, Skilled.</p><p><b>Technique Option:</b> Kairai Engeki: Shichihenge, Chakra no Ito.</p>"
